      <p>(Entorno de ejecución para JavaScript)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="node-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fundamentos y arquitectura de Node.js</li>
        <li>Ejemplos de servidores y scripts</li>
        <li>Manejo de paquetes y npm</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="node-quote">"Node.js permite llevar JavaScript al backend."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.node-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.node-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.node-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #339933;
}
.node-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #339933;
}
.node-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.node-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #339933;
}
.node-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.node-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.node-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #e6f7ec;
  border-left: 4px solid #339933;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #1d5c2f;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #339933 0%, #6fcf97 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #33993322;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6fcf97 0%, #339933 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #33993344;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .node-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .node-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
